e Vorstellungen und Konventionen im Wertesystem der hochmittelalterlichen Gesellschaft Islands reflektieren.   aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 08. Jul 2019) 0aClothing and dress in literature. 0aOld Norse literaturexHistory and criticism. 0aSagasxHistory and criticism. 4aIceland, Icelandic sagas, the Middle Ages. 4aIsland. 4aIsländersagas. 4aMittelalter. 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / European / Scandinavian.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDGBA Philosophy 2000 - 2014z9783110636949oZDB-23-GPH08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK GESAMTPAKET / COMPLETE PACKAGE 2013z9783110317350oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertE-BOOK PAKET LITERATURWISSENSCHAFT  2013z9783110317251oZDB-23-DLW0 cprintz978311033081640uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/9783110330915423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9783110330915.jpg  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_HICS  aEBA_CL_LT  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA14ALL  aPDA16SSH  aPDA1ALL  aPDA2  aPDA2HUM  aPDA5EBK  aZDB-23-DGGb2013  aZDB-23-DLWb2013  aZDB-23-GPHc2000d2014